{"SHAPABLE":[{"def":"That may be shaped.","pos":""}],"SHAPE":[{"def":"To form or create; especially, to mold or make into a particular form; to give proper form or figure to.","pos":""},{"def":"To adapt to a purpose; to regulate; to adjust; to direct; as, to shape the course of a vessel.","pos":""}],"SHAPELESS":[{"def":"Destitute of shape or regular form; wanting symmetry of dimensions; misshapen; -- opposed to Ant: shapely.","pos":""}],"SHAPELINESS":[{"def":"The quality or state of being shapely.","pos":""}],"SHAPELY":[{"def":"Well-formed; having a regular shape; comely; symmetrical.","pos":""}],"SHAPER":[{"def":"One who shapes; as, the shaper of one's fortunes.","pos":""},{"def":"That which shapes; a machine for giving a particular form or outline to an object.","pos":""}],"SHAPS":[{"def":"A pair of gorgeous buckskin shaps, embroidered up the sides and adorned with innumerable ermine skins.","pos":""}]}